{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/portfolio/national-roofing/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"edb39394-d57c-5e3d-bf50-d0aaea76d1f6","html":"<p>National Roofing is one of the leading Commercial Roofers in New Mexico, servicing most of the South West.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-problem\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-problem\" aria-label=\"the problem permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Problem:</h2>\n<p>National's site was initially built on Wix. All of the content was outdated, it wasn't easy to maintain at all, and they were in dire need of a full site rebuild.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-solution\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-solution\" aria-label=\"the solution permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Solution:</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"centerscrap-everything-and-start-overcenter\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#centerscrap-everything-and-start-overcenter\" aria-label=\"centerscrap everything and start overcenter permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><center>Scrap Everything and Start Over.</center></h3>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"the-process\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-process\" aria-label=\"the process permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Process</h2>\n<p>Over the duration of the project, I worked with several key people in the company to ensure the site was going to meet the needs of everyone who had a say. I started with a rough mockup of the design, in order to quickly get a plan locked into place.</p>\n<p>Once the design was approved, I started working on both the base theme code as well as the illustration that I was going to eventually animate for the homepage.</p>\n<h2 id=\"the-illustration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#the-illustration\" aria-label=\"the illustration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>The Illustration</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"National Roofing is Coming Home Illustration\"\n        title=\"National Roofing is Coming Home Illustration\"\n        src=\"/static/8a3fdecb975363b3cf28cc3636cd9725/c1b63/national-roofing-illustration.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a3fdecb975363b3cf28cc3636cd9725/5a46d/national-roofing-illustration.png 300w,\n/static/8a3fdecb975363b3cf28cc3636cd9725/0a47e/national-roofing-illustration.png 600w,\n/static/8a3fdecb975363b3cf28cc3636cd9725/c1b63/national-roofing-illustration.png 1200w,\n/static/8a3fdecb975363b3cf28cc3636cd9725/5b795/national-roofing-illustration.png 1455w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>National Roofing was in the process of bringing their years of commercial roofing experience to the residential market. I designed an illustration for animation of a crane slamming a roof onto a house.</p>\n<p>The house is in the style of a traditional New Mexico adobe house, and when the roof lands on the house, the illustration switches from black and white to color. Check it out on <a href=\"https://nationalroofing.com\">NationalRoofing.com</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"built-on-wordpress\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#built-on-wordpress\" aria-label=\"built on wordpress permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Built On WordPress</h2>\n<p>They wanted an easy way to add and update content as the site grew. I built out custom post types for their different Services, Projects, Testimonies &#x26; more. Their main complaint about their old site was all the work required to update the content. With WordPress, updating anything on the site is as easy as posting to Facebook.</p>\n<h2 id=\"continuous-integration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#continuous-integration\" aria-label=\"continuous integration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Continuous Integration</h2>\n<p>I knew that they were going to have me continue updating the site, so I set up their repo with a GitHub Action that updates the theme on their site <a href=\"/blog/tags/automation/\">automatically</a>.</p>","wordCount":{"words":308},"frontmatter":{"title":"National Roofing","description":"Custom WordPress Site","color":"#0087ce","date":"December 13, 2022","tags":["WordPress","Animation","React","Automation"],"images":[{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/8559e/national-roofing-homepage.png","srcSet":"/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/e3356/national-roofing-homepage.png 200w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/b705a/national-roofing-homepage.png 400w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/8559e/national-roofing-homepage.png 800w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/c11dd/national-roofing-homepage.png 1600w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/fd7d4/national-roofing-homepage.webp 200w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/6038d/national-roofing-homepage.webp 400w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/d53e3/national-roofing-homepage.webp 800w,\n/static/2c3d8ce4fc72d452958c1ece5de1c30c/f442d/national-roofing-homepage.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":800,"height":1741}}},{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/c34e5/national-roofing-homepage-mobile.png","srcSet":"/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/015ec/national-roofing-homepage-mobile.png 200w,\n/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/b4acf/national-roofing-homepage-mobile.png 400w,\n/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/c34e5/national-roofing-homepage-mobile.png 800w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/ab670/national-roofing-homepage-mobile.webp 200w,\n/static/25c699b8ec6cadf866ba491fefb6ed8f/6f531/national-roofin